  framework_2 = "W3C OWL2 owl:deprecated property + Semantic Versioning DEPRECATED annotation. CITED-AND-MOVED-ON: both use a single boolean flag; atlas.n6's [DEPRECATED YYYY-MM-DD] / [RETIRED YYYY-MM-DD] / [RETIRED_INCONCLUSIVE] / [SUPERSEDED] quartet is FINER than either, with date stamping not present in OWL2."
  framework_3 = "RFC 8174 BCP 14 'OBSOLETES' header (RFC supersession registry). CITED-AND-MOVED-ON: RFC OBSOLETES is also a forward-pointer between document IDs — atlas.n6's superseded_by has the same shape but operates on @-row slugs, not document numbers. PRECEDENT, not import."
